Topic sentence 1:
As a user on this movie prediction website, I want to have a simple “search” button that can be clicked on to in order to search a movie and get its average score result.

Happy path 1:
After typing in my movie name, I would like to have one button that can do the prediction for me at just one click. 
In this way, I can easily and quickly obtain an average score for the movie that I searched.

Exception:
In the case of exception, such as not typing in the correct movie name when clicked on the "search" button, there will not be any result in display.

Why is this function important for our app?
It shows the final result/score based on the input given by users, so it is crucial because it is what they really want to get by using our app.
